# 1D conv

This is a custom-made neural network featuring a semi-large 1-dimensional convolution layer, specifically crafted for testing purposes.

[Download input data](https://github.com/zkonduit/ezkl/blob/main/examples/onnx/1d_conv/input.json)
[Download model](https://github.com/zkonduit/ezkl/blob/main/examples/onnx/1d_conv/network.onnx)

Download the model and input data from the above links and place them in this folder.
